RESOURCE.STRING: Electric Fuel Lift Pump Override Test
This test can be used to validate the operation of the Electric Lift Pump by turning it off and on without the engine running.
Instructions:

Initial Conditions 
1. Engine stopped 
Steps 
1. Select Start 
2. Select Commanded Lift Pump Position 
3. The test will stop automatically 
Additional Information 
1. Test will stop when Allowed Test Time Remaining reaches zero 
2. If required, select Stop to end the test early
The calibration does not support the Electric Fuel Lift Pump Override Test.
